languages.text: [Напасть] "Знаешь, что вижу я? Ересь. Эти "экспонаты" должны гореть... и ты — вместе с ними!"
[Attack] "Do you know what I see? Heresy. These 'exhibits' must burn... and you will burn along with them!"
languages.original_text: [Напасть] "Знаешь, что вижу я? Ересь. Эти "экспонаты" должны гореть... и ты — вместе с ними!"

traits.locale_text: [Attack] "You see this as a means of entertaining the ignorant and lining your pockets. Do you know what I see? Heresy. These 'exhibits' must burn... and so must you!"

languages.text: [攻撃する]「これは明らかな異端だ。この『展示品』は燃やさねばならない…お前も奴らと一緒に燃やしてやる！」
languages.original_text: [Attack] "Do you know what I see? Heresy. These 'exhibits' must burn... and you will burn along with them!"

traits.locale_text: [攻撃する]「これは明らかな異端だ。この『展示品』は燃やさねばならない…お前も奴らと一緒に燃やしてやる！」

languages.text: [攻击]“你知道我看到了什么吗？我看到了异端。这些‘展品’必须被烧掉……你也要一起烧死！”
languages.original_text: [Attack] "Do you know what I see? Heresy. These 'exhibits' must burn... and you will burn along with them!"

languages.text: [Atacar] «¿Sabes lo que veo yo? Herejía. Estos "ejemplares" deben arder... ¡y tú con ellos!».
languages.original_text: [Attack] "Do you know what I see? Heresy. These 'exhibits' must burn... and you will burn along with them!"

languages.text: [Attaquer] « Vous savez comment j'appelle tout ceci ? De l'hérésie. Cette "ménagerie" doit être exterminée... et vous avec ! »

languages.text: [Saldır] "Bence bu ne, biliyor musun? Kâfirlik. Bu 'sergi' ateşe verilecek, sen de beraberinde yanacaksın!"
